13 male admissa: ‘admissum’ as a noun is rare. Cf. Liv. XXV 23 tale admissum and Tac. H. IV 4 cunctis sub Nerone admissis Ann. XI 4 de admissis Poppaeae. ‘ Male ’ is superfluous, as ‘admissum' is used only in malam partem.
